	Let us welcome you to the Playbill Dining Room with some great food, the usual warm hospitality, and live piano entertainment.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Our Executive Chef has prepared an impressive menu with fresh seasonal salads, delicious starters, choice of entrées and some delectable desserts! Our ever-so-popular buffet options include dinner, lunch and brunch – available on select days.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Complement this array of culinary delights with a beverage from our specialty menu of wines, beers, and estate ciders.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>NEW THIS YEAR:  We've simplified our lunch buffet to keep it delicious while offering it at a more affordable price.  You can still enjoy a satisfying selection of soups, salads, hot entrees, and delectable desserts!  Complement your meal with a beverage from our specialty menu of wines, beers, and estate ciders.
""";
